cladeNodeAttrKeys.name: Nextclade_pango
cladeNodeAttrKeys.description: Pango lineage as inferred by Nextclade from the nearest neighbour in the reference tree. 98% accurate for recent sequences, for higher accuracy use dedicated pangolin software in UShER or pangoLEARN mode. Recombinants may get (wrongly) assigned to a designated recombinant lineage if they have similar breakpoints.
